summary: An illustrated collection of all vanilla objects you can use in the Creation Kit
descriptionHtml:
[center][b][u]Skyrim Object Catalog by azraelb[/u][/b][/center]

Did you ever have problems finding the right objects in the Creation Kit?
If your answer is \"yes\" - this could be the solution for your problem:

The \"Skyrim Object Catalog\" is an illustrated collection of all vanilla objects available in the Skyrim Creation Kit. I grouped all objects in a new (at least for me) more logical menu index to to make searching more easy.

[b]This is an BETA-Version. There arent all objects listed at the moment.[/b]

[u]Version 0.1b contains:[/u]
- Most of the plants
- A lot of clutter-objects
- Few Landscape Objects

[i]This project is written in HTML and Javascript and is optimized for Firefox 11 and a 1920x1080 resolution.
If u dont use Firefox or another resolution the layout could look bad or the menu could not work at all (It wont work with IE, because IE needs an webserver for some AJAX features I used)[/i]

[u]Installation:[/u]
Simply extract the files and run index.html
author: azraelb
